requests.postData:
{"operationName":"Proposals","variables":{"space":"mimo.eth"},"query":"query Proposals($space: String!) {
  proposals(
    first: 20
    skip: 0
    where: {space_in: [$space]}
    orderBy: "created"
    orderDirection: desc
  ) {
    id
    title
    body
    type
    choices
    start
    end
    snapshot
    state
    created
    strategies {
      name
      params
      network
      __typename
    }
    author
    space {
      id
      name
      __typename
    }
    scores
    totalScores: scores_total
    votes
    __typename
  }
}
"}
